  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized clinical trial to assess acquisition and maintenance of paediatric asthma control
      through innovative devices supporting usual care. In the first study arm, a new application
      (DragONE) for iOS and Android will be only used for patient monitoring. In the second study
      arm, a small portable device (SmartONE) will also be connected to the DragONE APP, for daily
      assessment of the peak expiratory flow (PEF). The study duration is 12 weeks. The main
      outcome of the study is the Childhood Asthma Control Test (C-ACT) score, assessed once every
      4 weeks for 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
